TextEng: "What have the elders done to you?"
"How long have they been doing this to you?"
"Yes, well... Shoo! Get out of here..."
"What do you intend to do now?"
"What was that message you had to deliver?"
"You have no idea what to do, do you?"
"You're right. Get out of here. Shoo!"
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> "This is your chance to make things right."
"I've changed my mind. Get out of here. Shoo!"

Text: "신경 쓰지 마. 하고 싶은 대로 해."

TextEng: "There's a rebellion against the drow and the rebel camp needs your protection."
Text: "드로우에 맞서는 반란이 있어. 반란군 캠프가 네 보호를 필요로 해."

TextEng: "Okay, I freed you. How about a reward?"
"I have a geas placed on me and I need your help."
Text: "나한테 기아스가 걸려 있어. 네 도움이 필요해."

TextEng: "Don't kick a gift horse in the mouth..."
"You've still got a mission to accomplish, remember?"
"I need to ask one last favor of you."
